social_posts.post_text: Unlike the Super BOWL, SuperCROSS was a fair lead blown 🤙🏍️

I’ve been working for this grand vision of what I thought my life would look like.  I thought I would find this big “ah-ha” moment in my career where I look back in pride at something I’m doing or building and say to myself “THIS is what God made me for.”

I’ve tried many things over the short term of my life and I’ve never fully felt “talented” or “natural” at anything that sits right with my gut.

God works in very unexpected ways, he writes with crooked lines, and somehow always makes the circle come whole in the most wholesome way.

When looking in retrospect I realize that every step of my life has prepared and built me to take on this beautifully amazing journey with these two gorgeous gals 🤩 and to walk through this journey together 🫶

THIS, I was made for! And this, I feel was made for me 🙂 (so I’m claiming it as my own 😘🤣)

McKayle, you guide me as a loving best friend and I couldn’t be more grateful to God for walking you into my life, especially at the time that He did ❤️ thank you for loving me and showing me what real mature love is.

Esther Kate, I’m looking forward to playing with and helping guide you through our life 💕

And a shoutout to your family and the way they endlessly love me, my family, and even our close friends that have been with us since school 🥰 

Thank God he landed me here :) grateful is the word, peaceful is the feeling ☺️💛

Here’s to forever! 🤪❤️🫶

Eeeek! Am I excited to be your husband ☺️💕

I love y’all! ❤️

Locked and loaded 🔐
Summer 2023 ✅
Summer 2024 - coming soon! ⏳

Happy Birthday Esther Kate Mitchell! I love being your step daddy and look forward to watching you grow up 💕 thank you for being an absolute blessing to my life! 🙏✨🙌

And thank you to everyone that has shaped me into being a step dad 😊 you all know who you are 🙏♥️ very grateful on this day!

I married my best friend 🥰🤍 and made another best friend along the way 😊
I’m amazed that God brought us together… after going on 9 years of friendship, after both going our separate ways and living our own lives, God somehow brought us together and made the most beautiful piece of my life 🙂 
Yin and Yang, It feels like we fit like a puzzle.
McKayle, you and your mama have taught me what real forgiveness and mercy are.  God has touched my heart and saved my soul without a doubt through your loving nature & you in fact have been my safe place throughout the past year.
Esther Kate, I may have fallen more in love with being part of your life than anything this world has ever brought me 🙂💛 our sweet bond brings joy to my heart every single day that I get to experience you living
“My peace is grand, my love and faith is grander.”

Nobody else I’d rather be welded to 💛 I thank God for you McKayle and Esther Kate every day 🫶

The most pure joy has come from a Godly relationship and evolving into a father 🙂

Shoutout @katiebertagnolli AGAIN with an phenomenal unique touch to capture our most precious memories ❤️
